<br>
So I decided to test it.  I ran around pickpocketing the same mob for about an hour.  after getting normal drop off of it on around the tenth try, nothing for the rest of the hour.  Then I killed it and got a trivial message.<br>
<br>
This was before the patch that fixed the 'phantom no-drop' bug with TLC.  Now that those items are no longer TLC, it doesn't affect the pickpocketting.<br>
<br>
What I'm saying is, even though it doesn't really matter, TLC does affect pickpocketting. <p>Denoi Fishwhiskers<BR>
